span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>At EMI, we have spent more than 10 years creating content focused on helping engineering professionals become better managers and leaders.\u00a0 We have <a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/podcasts\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">9\u00a0Podcasts<\/a>, 3 YouTube Channels (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/EngineeringCareers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Leadership<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCcUwvohzlYBMYuyEwLyMvcg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FE Exam<\/a>, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCUaCcvfn0nD2lY9ZAxYcXRQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PE Exam<\/a>) and an active <a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/category\/blog\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">weekly blog<\/a>.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Subscribe to our weekly newsletter (in the right hand column of this page)<\/strong> to get our latest content delivered to your inbox in a weekly summary email.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These skills will differentiate you in your career and help you to be a well rounded engineering professional.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The market is too competitive to be one-dimensional.\u00a0 We\u2019re here to help.<\/span><\/p><p>The headings below will take you to the content that most interests you or you can scroll right down this page and browse.<\/p><h4><em>Complimentary Comprehensive Engineering Career Guides<\/em><\/h4><p><a href=\"http:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/book\/\">Engineer Your Own Success: 7 Key Elements to Creating an Extraordinary Engineering Career (Book)<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"http:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/2013\/10\/10\/create-extraordinary-engineering-career-anthony-fasanos-complete-engineering-career-guide\/\">How to Create an Extraordinary Engineering Career \u2013 Anthony Fasano\u2019s Complete Engineering Career Guide<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"http:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/2014\/10\/09\/ugly-truth-behind-fundamentals-engineering-exam-fe-exam-can-finally-crush-less-time-think\/\">The Ugly Truth Behind the Fundamentals of Engineering Exam (FE Exam) and How You Can Finally Crush It in Less Time Thank You Think<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"http:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/2014\/07\/22\/pe-exam-prep-guide-can-pass-pe-exam-without-study-everything\/\">PE Exam Prep Guide: How You Can Pass the PE Exam without Having to Study \u201cEverything\u201d<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"http:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/2013\/12\/20\/wow-crowd-engineers-guide-public-speaking\/\">Wow the Crowd: Anthony Fasano\u2019s Guide to Public Speaking for Engineers<\/a><\/p>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"7f4f96d9","settings":{"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","background_background":"classic","background_image":{"url":"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/AdobeStock_912059643.jpg","id":65546,"size":"","alt":"","source":"library"},"background_position":"center center","background_repeat":"no-repeat","background_size":"cover","pa_condition_repeater":[]},"elements":[{"id":"21b8a51b","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null,"background_background":"classic","background_color":"#0000006B","padding":{"unit":"px","top":"20","right":"0","bottom":"20","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"6598dd87","settings":{"editor":"<p>Sharpen your skills with our resources<\/p>","align":"center","text_color":"#FFFFFF","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px",